MEC Ravi Pillay, Kwazulu-Natal Economic Development, Tourism and Environmental Affairs launched the 16 Days of Activism for No Violence Against Women and Children Campaign in uMgungundlovu District, on 25 November. The launch was attended by civil society formations, traditional leaders and mayors within the uMgungundlovu District. The march started at Chapel Street and ended at the Pietermaritzburg Town Hall.